http://school.discovery.com/ontv/ad.html

NEXT WEEK ON TLC ELEMENTARY SCHOOL
Matter and Energy
http://school.discovery.com/ontv/tlc.html
Discover how water molecules change states, from solid to liquid and gas.=
 Then
learn how pressure affects the human body underwater, at the highest points=
 on
Earth, and while traveling through outer space. Finally, measure heat by=20
learning
about Fahrenheit, Celsius, and Kelvin.
Airs: Friday 1/17/03

Airs on The Learning Channel every Friday at 8:30 a.m. ET. As a service of=
=20
Discovery Channel with Cable in the Classroom, each program is commercial=20
free and can be taped and used in the classroom for up to two years.

